Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Weather Report
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather report?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, actually, I'm really into\Nthis weather girl right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Yuriko Hyuga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here at the fountain plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,See? That's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she definitely looks like your type.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as long as you like watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow, we'll finally\Nbe getting some more snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to see a real rise in temperature,\Nwhich means it's going to be a cold day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone, I hope you'll all\Nstay warm, and good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a live broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's insane. What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The overlapping moments
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We might believe them to be eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.09,0:01:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The labyrinthine sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Begs for light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The impulse eats away at me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Libido erases my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Into darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have fallen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a hideous form
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If my human tears have dried
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Our crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NOur crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wets our bond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NWe share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we two live on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Licking each other's wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Defining each other's life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirsting for love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Plan B
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagi, sedative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a high-performance gas mask.\NIt blocks out odors and colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling all Public Security Division 5 personnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Level 5 Vampire Incident in progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispatch human officers to the fountain plaza\Nin Ikebukuro West Gate Park immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim is bleeding profusely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It took place during the live weather broadcast,\Nthere were several onlookers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that devils have witnessed\Nthe event and have transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm taking a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go stop that devil in the knit cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If he keeps drinking her blood, she'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They've probably stopped the cameras,\Nso I'll be back in about three...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Make that one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm going to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe a slasher would attack\Nduring a live TV broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And there happened to be a devil\Nright there watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Happened to be"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They did that broadcast every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that the attacker knew\Nthere was a devil on the crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the slasher wasn't trying to kill the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he wanted the devil to see human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils throughout the Kanto Region are\Ntransforming after witnessing the attack on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation is getting out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anybody call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or an ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tie him up, so somebody-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking down a monster like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You better kill him, just in case.\NI mean, look at that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop filming. This isn't a show,\Nand I'm not killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, just kill him already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Run. Get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where... can I run?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I think the monster's going after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll be safe if we just get away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Another monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki, this is Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have Tsukasa Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come pick her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a status-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take these. They're sedatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever get attacked when\Nyou're alone again, you can inject the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to give someone an injection!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take the needle and stab-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That devil back there scratched me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing a gas mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make out the color or the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think of it as blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hide the scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need me to, I'll find somewhere\Nto wash the blood off right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't disappear again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I need one of those sedatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you inject me in ten seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you might feel a prick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Might feel a prick"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry. Did it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll be able to move much\Nfor about ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll have to wait here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:07:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you... do that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Makimura, B Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A unit has fired his gun at a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe that the devil was\Namong the audience and had transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The officer is in shock.\NHe likely did not know about devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently a cop shot a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with the police! Everyone, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the gun down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see anyone who looks unusual,\Ndo not get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Report to us immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When I can move again, I'll take you and we'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but... Lee is still down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you and he... close?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to that alley,\Nand I happened to run into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he dropped his cross\Nand he was looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him I was looking for you,\Nand he said he would help me find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what was on his necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A long, black cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the symbol of ONLO, the orphanage I grew up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's near Obihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They take in devil orphans and raise them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better not to talk about this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't bother me that much, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know very much about you, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm happy to learn that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! But you don't have to tell me\Nanything you don't want voo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Want voo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since you hit me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish he would laugh more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If he had a cross like this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's a strong possibility\Nwe're from the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But there weren't any foreigners\Nlike him in my age group.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other kids were all devils;\NI was the only one who was half.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are half-devils that unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Having only one devil parent is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that... even be possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils can't have sex with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no way to conceive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a half-devil child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you stand being around me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I attacked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have killed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I might not be a half!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I might just be a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um! That is, I mean, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it really matters...\Nif you're half or full-devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,or if you're just human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't change the fact that you are Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more worried about whether or not\NI'm a good match for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The TV was saying something about vampires!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The sedative hasn't worn off yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My knees... are giving out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, grab the handrail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you'll fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure do fall a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure you have devil blood in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your physical abilities are pretty weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just because I gave him\Na sedative a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know that, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really a half?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're wrapping things up\Nover by Ikebukuro West Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Human personnel from each squad
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,will now go help contain the devil transformations\Nhappening throughout the region.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be informed that the investigation will be\Nassigned to human personnel only.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil personnel, please stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikuhura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone in F Squad alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all fine. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's been injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I was held up in traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is a civilian we found on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My guy's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai, say hello. You haven't met, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kikuhara, A Squad. A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about him scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I met you somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, maybe at the new staff ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Kikuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,About our next deployment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Sawazaki, I'll see you at the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something about Kikuhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,was unusually warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're both alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a fire going, so hurry on upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we have two extra people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tsukasa Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, your girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sakaki, the owner here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hans Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of Anzai and Tsukasa's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a witness in the sniper case and this new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him stay here until I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ms. Taira, I'll want to get\Nyour version of what happened, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have guest rooms available,\Nand the lounge is rather large.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, make yourselves comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I own the whole building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I rent out everything from the third floor up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any vacant rooms at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but Yuuki is one of my tenants,\Nso you could stay in his...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mess right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. I have to tell him\Nit's possible to get used to blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that make life a little easier for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we spend more time together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about blood tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you probably should tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Could help him live longer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Live longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil's average lifespan is only 39 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you really brought everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll want to set up an investigation committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll be back until after midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It is unclear whether they are\Nrelated to the Ikebukuro incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}I heard on the radio.\NIt is unclear whether they are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,related to the Ikebukuro incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It is unclear whether they are\Nrelated to the Ikebukuro incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}I knew they'd leave us devils\Nout of the decision-making eventually.\Nbut similar phenomena are occurring all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but similar phenomena are occurring all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Police are scrambling to handle the outbreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}This was the only line of work\Nwhere devils got any decent treatment.\NPolice are scrambling to handle the outbreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}This was the only line of work\Nwhere devils got any decent treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long before we're out of places to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know they're going to cut you all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't I? They always thought devils\Nwere tough to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're high maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Freaking out every time we see a little bit of bl-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have to keep spelling it out for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anything happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So just sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I almost attacked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagi, I want to ask you something. Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If Anzai isn't half-devil, if he's a full devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,can he develop a blood tolerance like Lee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help. You're making food, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we making?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say "midnight snack," you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm Tsukasa Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer Juliana Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a full devil.\NMy parents are American and Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nationality-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's an apron for each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just so pretty, like a Hollywood actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?\NIt's not flattering, it's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I just always admired beautiful,\Nsophisticated women... so, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let's stop this, Zero Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What good will it do to chase me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you were against Plan B!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was our leader's decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you bear no responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I ever say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,By sacrificing a few humans,\Nwe call attention to the existence of devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the vital first step in\Neliminating them from our society!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from me! Drop your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not carrying a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You trust humans too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is... I have another mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tried to interfere with Plan B...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. As long as you're around,\Nyou'll only get in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sex between a devil and a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tie up the devil, gag them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What about artificial insemination?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be even harder,\Nthe way things are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it bother you, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,However they were conceived,\Nthe child didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking a count for ramen flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Anzai, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You two stay here and make out\Nas long as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,devils usually only live 39 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know that devils are always\Ngoing without blood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me that lowers their life expectancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it. I've never seen any data\Non devil life expectancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The government never released any of those numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, when you got hurt,\Nyou drank blood and it healed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really trust-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee drinks a little blood every day\Nto get used to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so he can drink blood to heal\Nwhen he needs to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why his wounds heal, and he's so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And he can live longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,drink my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you some every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like softly melting away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could have loved each other more like that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I have told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance encounter that cannot amount to love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this filthy form is who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these fingers trembling as they touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of fighting together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hold you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect you without hurting you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You and only you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of desiring forever
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Against the urges surging up inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, again, I..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:22:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we're softly melting away...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that last job was hard on you, Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'd do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for the team and for you, Zero Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Murakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ren Murakami, unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.63,0:22:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Had been stalking weather reporter Yuriko Hyuga,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,attacked her out of resentment for\Nher failure to reciprocate his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But was struck by a guilty conscience\Nduring his escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,stabbed himself, and jumped off a building.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the entirety of Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A few sacrifices...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,will save society.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you need to kill Murakami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill humans, Kikuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We should only have to kill devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So. Before you die, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.55,0:23:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,look human to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,DEVILS' LINE:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Line 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.76,0:23:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dogmatic."
